To install:

1) Check you have the Perl Win32::Services, Net::SMTP and Win32
   modules installed
2) Change the various variables within ServiceMonitor.pl as
   required to point at the services you require monitoring, the
   path to the state file and optionally mail servers and and
   admin email addresses (these are lines 44-54)
3) Use the instsrv and srvany tools to create ServiceMonitor.pl
   as a service as described at
   http://www.techeez.com/windows_tips/service_under_nt.htm

The latest version of ServiceMonitor can always be found at
<http://www.nth-dimension.org.uk/>.
